data.name: label10.Text
data.value:
Remote Access Tool wasn't created for illegal usage but to help shuting down - restarting - sending messages - stoping processes - starting processes on another computer.
==============================HELP=============================== In order to shutdown a process at the Tasks menu you need to check the check box at the left of the process you want to kill. If there are multiple processes of the same program like chrome, in order to kill it you need to kill one process at a time because some processes recall themselves before they die, therefore nothing happens. When you start a process make sure to type the .exe extention of the program you want to initialize! Don't disconnect the server if you want to do something else with the clients because they won't get reconnected after they are disconnected! So make sure to complete all the actions you want before you shutdown the server.
